---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';


---

<Layout title='About Astro'>
    <h1>About Astro</h1>
    <p>
        Astro is a new kind of static site generator that delivers lightning-fast performance and
        remarkable developer experience. Astro sites load in milliseconds and ship only the
        critical HTML, CSS, and JavaScript needed to render the page. Astro is built with modern
        JavaScript and supports popular frameworks like React, Vue, Svelte, and Preact.
    </p>
    <p>
        With Astro, you can build sites with your favorite JavaScript framework, use your favorite
        libraries, and even import components from npm. Astro is designed to be flexible and
        developer-friendly, so you can build sites the way you want to.
    </p>
    <p>
        To learn more about Astro, visit the{' '}
        <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Astro website
        </a>
        .
    </p>
</Layout>